name: Mini Heart Notebooks
description:
Each mini notebook has a little over 30 blank pages. They are about 2.5" in diameter in the middle. Use them to write inspiring quotes, as mini scrapbooks (perfect for inchies!) or anything else you can think of!

At only $1 each, you should probably buy all 3 colors!

name: Love Birds Tags
description:
Set of 6 tags handmade with high quality supplies! (All other items in photos are for display purposes only.) Tags are a maroonish/ reddish color with a punched circle with the words "cheep", "love" & "nest" printed on it. The birds are popped up with pop dots & the tag is tied with abaca twine. 

Write on the back with a gel pen or on the included white circles & then stick them to the back. Tags will also look great on your scrapbook pages or use them to label your supplies!

name: Kiss Me Tickets
description:
Leave one for your love to find each day of the week leading up to Valentine's Day/ their birthday/ your anniversary, etc. Leave a hint to their gift on the back & have them save the ticket to be later redeemed for a kiss! Or make them into a booklet, write reasons why you love your sweetheart on the back & let them redeem the tickets when they want. 

This listing is for a set of 7 hand stamped tickets. The back is covered with red card stock & is left blank for your message.

Love the earth by buying something recycled! These are stamped on the inside of a cereal box!

name: Heart Confetti
description:
Make any card or letter more fun by adding confetti to the envelope! You get approximately 300, 1" hearts. That's about enough confetti for 15-30 cards (depending how many you use per envelope). The confetti comes with assorted designs & some have glitter or are double-sided.

The pink/red hearts are perfect for Valentine's Day cards, Sweet 16 invites or girl birth announcements. Use the blue for boy birth announcements, party invites or just because! The green hearts are perfect for St. Patrick's Day party invites or cards.

name: Punny Valentine's
description:
This listing is for a set of 4 valentine/ Love pop-up mini cards. They are handmade of high quality materials. Foam dots are used to pop-up a part of each paper-pieced image. The cards measure approximately 2.5 x 2.5". The inside of the cards have these sayings stamped with black ink: "warm & cozy" (house), "You make my heart flutter" (butterfly), "love you with a cherry on top" (ice cream) & "you're so sweet" (cupcake). They do not come with envelopes.

Use them as gift tags, thank you's for your shop, lunch notes or leave them around with a private message for your loved one to find. 

If you'd like these cards in a different color or without a message, please let me know in the "Add special instructions to merchant" box in PayPal.
